data.description: This is a great 3-bedroom 2 bath home located on approximately 3/4 of an acre in Monroe's Swartz school district! The home features a spacious living area with cathedral-style ceiling, stone wood burning fireplace, covered patio, double carport, and large fenced back yard. Has so much potential and qualifies for Rural Development so come see it before it’s too late! All information deemed reliable. Buyers’ agent to verify.
